'''致死量'''（'''{{lang-en|lethal dose}}'''、簡寫為 '''{{lang|en|LD}}'''）是指特定物質或是[[輻射|輻射]]可造成[[死亡|死亡]]的量。對於不同的[[動物|動物]]，或是其他條件差異（如年齡、健康狀態等）而言，同一物質所能致死的量並不一定。

這些數值多數是來自[[動物實驗|動物實驗]]，鮮少有紀錄是來自[[人類|人類]]。<ref>{{Cite web| date =2011-06-24| title = Allergan Receives FDA Approval for First-of-Its-Kind, Fully in vitro, Cell-Based Assay for BOTOX® and BOTOX® Cosmetic (onabotulinumtoxinA)| publisher = [[Source:_Allergan,_Inc._News_Provided_by_Acquire_Media|Source: Allergan, Inc. News Provided by Acquire Media]]| url = http://agn.client.shareholder.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=587234| accessdate = 2011-06-26| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110626185759/http://agn.client.shareholder.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=587234| archivedate = 2011年6月26日}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| title = Vision and Roadmap for the 21st Century| publisher = [[Source:_National_Toxicology_Program|Source: National Toxicology Program]]| url = http://ntp.niehs.nih.gov/go/vision| accessdate = 2011-10-29| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081012173524/http://ntp.niehs.nih.gov/go/vision| archivedate = 2008-10-12}}</ref>

致死量可分為[[半數致死量|半數致死量]]（LD<sub>50</sub>）和最低致死量（LD<sub>Lo</sub>），半數致死量指的是能殺死一半試驗總體的劑量，最低致死量指的是能殺死一個生物所需要的最低藥物劑量<ref>[http://www.ccohs.ca/oshanswers/chemicals/ld50.html What is an LD50 and LC50] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626013647/http://www.ccohs.ca/oshanswers/chemicals/ld50.html |date=2015-06-26 }}</ref>

